author: neilg
msg: fix segfault on GCC 2.9x.  The depreacted DOM attribute implementation had a cute trick where a void * field could be either a NodeChild pointer or a DOMString; the latter played havoc with the new memory management paradigm.  Now a union of a DOMString * and a ChildNode * is used.
